1.14
log
@remove use of BITS and BIT macros
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: rtwreg.h,v 1.13 2006/01/05 05:40:35 jsg Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: rtwreg.h,v 1.12 2005/01/16 11:50:43 dyoung Exp $	*/
/*-
